---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
---
<Layout title="About KP - Kylo Parisher" description="Professional biography and public values for Kylo Parisher / KP.">
<section class="prose max-w-none rounded-[2rem] bg-base-200 p-8 shadow-xl"><h1>About Kylo Parisher / KP</h1><p>{profile.summary}</p><p>KP connects cybersecurity, AI/ML, secure infrastructure, autonomous-agent workflows, space-systems research, and education through one consistent practice: make systems understandable, resilient, reviewable, and safe to discuss in public.</p><h2>Mission</h2><p>Build intelligent systems that help people reason about risk, delivery, and collaboration without depending on secret runtime state or unverifiable claims.</p><h2>Public values</h2><ul><li>Protect secrets and private operational context.</li><li>Prefer accessible, static-first content before client-side effects.</li><li>Label evidence levels, limitations, and research concepts honestly.</li><li>Use PR-CYBR/spec-bootstrap-style branch and CI discipline where appropriate.</li></ul><h2>Public-safe overview</h2><p>PR-CYBR and G8 references are presented as public portfolio context, governance, research, and design language unless a public repository or document verifies implementation details.</p></section>
</Layout>
